### Global Element Styles

```css
/* styles/globals.css */
*,
*::before,
*::after {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
  color: var(--color-text);
  background-color: var(--color-bg);
  line-height: 1.5;
}

/* Focus styles for accessibility */
:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--color-border-focus);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* Buttons */
button {
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: inherit;
  font-size: inherit;
}

button:disabled {
  cursor: not-allowed;
  opacity: 0.6;
}

/* Form elements */
input,
textarea,
select {
  font-family: inherit;
  font-size: inherit;
}
```

